{"tid":1615853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］ 打擊紅色資本 救救本土小店","createTime":"2019-10-03T08:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:28:35.000Z","uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce555c49d68b881aa938cc33cc62a0671f3cb0b0","tid":1615853,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:20:00.000Z","msg":"紅色資本企業 作為香港上市或經營企業 <br />\n不斷滲透本港資源 侵蝕香港文化<br />\n為獨裁政權站台 指責本港示威抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n紅色資本 開鋪做勢 上市吸血 侵佔物業 壓迫港人<br />\n<br />\n我地必須驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\n罷買所有紅色資本企業 支援本土小店經營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff4beaa6e13e445b9ad5ec4930c444edd37f07a","tid":1615853,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"唔好再沉迷打狗 我地已經搵到終極大佬！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65f44ba85613d53c9a4325ee928d3826c4cfb59d","tid":1615853,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"打倒紅資 你我做起"},{"pid":"c9966911952572a7ce83519afd89bc342e71e93d","tid":1615853,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"擊退紅資 人人有責"},{"pid":"e8b84708dfa2f0c9c61b2917341052cd8798fc25","tid":1615853,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:22:20.000Z","msg":"已經搵返失散大佬 齊齊錫錫共黨春袋"},{"pid":"a54ec04823328eaee343e4311344b83b377f1d8c","tid":1615853,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"對準紅資 藍鶳黃絲"},{"pid":"d4e3e902d012ab93703699af72879b2389deb08c","tid":1615853,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"657e184735bebfec2bbf11be5803b3e64b522d62","tid":1615853,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}